{"tid":1578801,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"十點大叫係咪永久取消？","createTime":"2019-09-18T09:31:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T11:19:31.000Z","uid":26876,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"00670f80a55bc2e78f993d31cbdec437c1a678d7","tid":1578801,"uid":26876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:31:15.000Z","msg":"無曬人叫"},{"pid":"669c2073776ded20a4b763ef104902bc660b0736","tid":1578801,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:31:38.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全球響應「929全球集會抗赤納粹」</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全世界一齊對準極權！</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1577380\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1577380</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hWqVmOV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhWqVmOV.jpg&h=075c7745&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n1tov9s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn1tov9s.png&h=0af09f95&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"88dfd869248e2718f424926ca761d63fe541eecc","tid":1578801,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:32:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93db056d2ea2948c04a773005b58cddc2f1d7d6f","tid":1578801,"uid":94575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:32:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e259f21a07b40a2cea3709e781ce355fdc2f5bc7","tid":1578801,"uid":67023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:32:57.000Z","msg":"我得閒都會叫，但係無人應<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7319c687cc9d69b5b631675b8748a9a4265a02eb","tid":1578801,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:33:31.000Z","msg":"【9.23~9.27】全球「反共」聯軍來了我帶路！快閃式萬國「民主」旗號召世界<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eccnjS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eccnjS</a><br />\n<blockquote><br />\n由於香港身為<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>東道主</strong></span></span>倘若因為任何原因而令到遊行人數小得難睇, 是不理想的！<br />\n<br />\n同埋我寧願<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>10.1國殤</strong></span>打到拆天就最好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當然大家請記著呢日唔是End-game<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 由美帝反共眾議員可以見到場戰爭並非一朝一夕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 失去所有勇武運動將難以持續<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家講到星期日9.29是全球性<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 單靠香港人文宣團隊twitter retweet比當地人是難以收到巨大宣傳效益<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">唯有無比juicy<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />方法去呼喚他國人民, 同埋件事夠juicy<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />外國媒體先會幫你免費頭版</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\"><strong>【9.23~9.27】全球「反共」聯軍來了我帶路！<br />\n集合時間：1930~2000<br />\n遊行時間：2000~終點和平散去 (預計9點前行到遮打即龍頭散去)<br />\n舉行日期：9月23日至9月27日晚上快閃式遊行<br />\n遊行路線：修頓球場 至 遮打花園<br />\n注意事項：遊行完就即時由中環遮打盡快散去！不起衝突！人小就行行人路<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n衣著：遊行時黑色, 前往及離開時非黑色<br />\n快閃遊行目的：號召全球「反共」聯軍同時響應9.29大遊行, 盡可能與香港同步舉行！</strong></span><br />\n利申：是次遊行屬自發性質, 沒有不反對通知書<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講到反共你走去申請唔好傻啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我主張每晚均可見到頭60名民主國度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只要有60位手足舉60支旗個畫面已經夠晒Juicy<br />\n首先你話該國家一直龜縮有咩撚用,舉嚟把撚啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但是9.29反共大遊行號召目標是各國人民,<br />\n如果我地真是連續一星期舉民主國家國旗, <span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>當地右翼會相當自豪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span>,<br />\n同埋每晚我地可以twitter開放檢討比各國人民知道其國旗在香港揚起以打倒中共</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e33f56a23b420be02e8004b564c03d9a3b4d9a2b","tid":1578801,"uid":1315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:33:33.000Z","msg":"我果邊好多人叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kiss.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dc9b719917b4d0bf74e1dda1e49b4e48dee602f","tid":1578801,"uid":5258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:33:34.000Z","msg":"推 今晚繼續"},{"pid":"f8b5b2be321c69c9d74f3dc215d1c2852dc61e54","tid":1578801,"uid":199553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:33:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2708677488a7baf20eb80ad0bf9088a26201ac46","tid":1578801,"uid":69929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e33f56a23b420be02e8004b564c03d9a3b4d9a2b","tid":1578801,"uid":1315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:33:33.000Z","msg":"我果邊好多人叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kiss.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:34:05.000Z","msg":"x2"},{"pid":"28f63d319b9dc941bbbaa125866054ce11fa2174","tid":1578801,"uid":11849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:34:06.000Z","msg":"宜家無人嗌<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b256de1cfcdca886c1add7c7d60e8c8f3ff50b7f","tid":1578801,"uid":215861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:37:02.000Z","msg":"屌 唔知邊條仆街話改9點<br />\n搞到9點10點都冇人嗌<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass